ér : [det.] definite ('the')
én : [det.] indefinite ('a'/'an')

ža : [det.] interrogative ('what', 'which')

dö : [prep.] ablative particle ### alt: dé
   - from, of
   - authorship
u : [prep.] at, in, near @@@

im : [prep] in (contained by, within the bounds of, part of, into)
-> imir : [v.] enter
-> imira : [n.] entry, input
ust : [prep.] out (outside of, away from, not in)
-> ustir : [v.] exit
- > ustira : [n.] exit, output

ot : up, high, top (of)
ös : down, low, bottom (of)
od : on (top of) @@@
öš : under @@@

mér : [adv.] comparative ('more')
mést : [adv.] superlative ('most')
lér : [adv.] diminutive comparative ('less')
lést : [adv.] diminutive superlative ('least')
té : [adv.] too, too much, too many

is
-- [n.] here
-- [det.] proximal demonstrative ('this')
üs
-- [n.] there
-- [det] distal demonstrative ('that')

ül : [adj.] (the) previous, anticedent 
-> üla : [adj.] before
-> ülna : [adj.] first, primordial

é : [cnjc.] and
mit : [cnjc.] with

gèšt : [prep.] against
ob : [prep.] on, on top of

sti : [prep. cnjc.] as if, like so, similar to
stit : [adv.] thus, in this way or manner

gèn : [cjnc.] when, during the time that, at the time of the action of the following clause
si : [cnjc.] if, in the case/condition that, given/supposing/assuming that

fas : [n.] front
dos : [n.] back
